close_prices <- Cl(AAPL)
open_prices <- Op(AAPL)
volume <- Vo(AAPL)

ma_short <- SMA(close_prices, n = 20)
ma_long <- SMA(close_prices, n = 50)

rsi <- RSI(close_prices, n = 14)
macd_vals <- MACD(close_prices, nFast = 12, nSlow = 26, nSig = 9, maType = EMA)

df <- data.frame(Date = index(AAPL),
                 Open = as.numeric(open_prices),
                 Close = as.numeric(close_prices),
                 Volume = as.numeric(volume),
                 MA20 = as.numeric(ma_short),
                 MA50 = as.numeric(ma_long),
                 RSI = as.numeric(rsi),
                 MACD = macd_vals$macd,
                 SignalLine = macd_vals$signal)

df <- df %>%
  mutate(Signal = case_when(
    lag(MA20) < lag(MA50) & MA20 >= MA50 ~ "BUY",
    lag(MA20) > lag(MA50) & MA20 <= MA50 ~ "SELL",
    TRUE ~ NA_character_
  ))


signals <- df %>% filter(!is.na(Signal) & !is.na(Date))

Wizualizacja

buy_dates <- signals$Date[signals$Signal == "BUY"]
sell_dates <- signals$Date[signals$Signal == "SELL"]
buy_prices <- signals$Close[signals$Signal == "BUY"]
sell_prices <- signals$Close[signals$Signal == "SELL"]

buy_dates <- buy_dates[!is.na(buy_dates)]
sell_dates <- sell_dates[!is.na(sell_dates)]

chartSeries(AAPL, type = "candlesticks", theme = chartTheme("white"),
            TA = NULL, name = "AAPL - analiza techniczna")

addTA(ma_short, col = "blue", on = 1)

addTA(ma_long, col = "red", on = 1)

if (length(buy_dates) > 0) {
  addTA(xts(rep(1, length(buy_dates)), order.by = buy_dates),
        on = 1, col = "green", type = "p", pch = 24, cex = 1.5)
}

if (length(sell_dates) > 0) {
  addTA(xts(rep(1, length(sell_dates)), order.by = sell_dates),
        on = 1, col = "red", type = "p", pch = 25, cex = 1.5)
}

addTA(rsi, col = "purple")
abline(h = 70, col = "red", lty = 2)
abline(h = 30, col = "green", lty = 2)

addTA(macd_vals$macd, col = "blue")

addTA(macd_vals$signal, col = "orange")

summary_df <- df %>%
  summarise(
    Średnia_cena = mean(Close),
    Max_cena = max(Close),
    Min_cena = min(Close),
    Liczba_sygnalów_BUY = sum(Signal == "BUY"),
    Liczba_sygnalów_SELL = sum(Signal == "SELL")
  )
